@Luap99. this is duo to Cirrus CI was launching too many VMs **concurrently** in `us-central1`, exceeding GCP's concurrent operations quota.
example: `│ 2026-03-05         │ 163               │` and major spike is on `21:00-22:00 UTC`.
there is 267 VM creation done by cirrus-ci over 1 hour.  and 110 operation **failed** duo to the rate limits. we are continuously seeing those errors.
